{"tid":1172500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警方: 六四遊行人數急增逾兩倍","createTime":"2019-05-26T13:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T09:07:51.000Z","uid":134071,"like":26,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"76002043e562a1738a6a8cfd6bce140a73156fe8","tid":1172500,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T13:01:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190526/s00001/1558865389064\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190526%2Fs00001%2F1558865389064&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18BSq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=76f7772e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190526%2Fs00001%2F1558865389064&h=a0656c79\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190526/s00001/1558865389064</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年5月26日星期日<br />\n<br />\n今年是六四事件30年，支聯會今午（26日）3時舉行「愛國民主大遊行」，由灣仔遊行至西環中聯辦，爭取平反六四，同時反對《逃犯條例》修例，遊行隊伍隊尾於黃昏6時抵達終點。<br />\n<br />\n支聯會表示，今日遊行人數超過2200人，較去年1100人多一倍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>警方表示，遊行最高峰有2100人參與，較警方去年數字610人，增逾兩倍。</strong><br />\n<br />\n支聯會副主席蔡耀昌遊行後表示，對人數上升感到高興，相信除六四30年因素外，亦因為香港人權狀况急劇惡化，《逃犯條例》修例令人權問題「殺到埋身」。他預料，今年會有更多市民出席支聯會六四燭光晚會。"},{"pid":"d9fc7d8ade12bed46ac7fe8ae229b1c9943685f8","tid":1172500,"uid":2429,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T13:03:35.000Z","msg":"蔡耀昌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ad80ee7ccdfd790fc98a125e5c55f2c433e289","tid":1172500,"uid":133680,"like":8,"dislike":16,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"d9fc7d8ade12bed46ac7fe8ae229b1c9943685f8","tid":1172500,"uid":2429,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T13:03:35.000Z","msg":"蔡耀昌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T13:04:59.000Z","msg":"台仰都話悼六四，班非統即獨，六四係鄰國事o既講獨派係咪扮睇唔到？<i